229
00:26:03,794 --> 00:26:06,991
Come on! Lets get out!
Come on!

230
00:26:13,203 --> 00:26:14,864
Lets go! Christ!

231
00:26:14,938 --> 00:26:15,905
<i>[Man] We're leaving</i>
<i>in just a few seconds.</i>

232
00:26:15,973 --> 00:26:20,774
Lets go! Why are we sitting here?
Why are we sitting here?

233
00:26:20,844 --> 00:26:24,177
- Sir, please! Look at me. Stay calm.
- Lets go!

234
00:26:55,345 --> 00:26:57,677
She's free, sir!
Go!

235
00:27:06,490 --> 00:27:09,050
Hope you know how
to fold this, sir.

236
00:27:09,126 --> 00:27:11,458
Thank you, Colonel.
I'll never forget this.

237
00:27:11,528 --> 00:27:14,361
Sir.

238
00:27:19,403 --> 00:27:21,337
Go!

239
00:27:33,116 --> 00:27:35,050
[Groaning]

240
00:27:41,458 --> 00:27:43,392
[Panting]

241
00:28:06,149 --> 00:28:11,451
- [Grunting, Groaning]
- <i>[Man] Krasevitch is hit!</i>

242
00:28:13,657 --> 00:28:18,219
<i>Corpsman! Corpsman!</i>
<i>Shit!</i>

243
00:28:18,295 --> 00:28:21,059
Goddamn it!

244
00:28:21,131 --> 00:28:23,065
Fuck!

245
00:28:28,939 --> 00:28:30,873
Six, Red Man.

246
00:28:30,941 --> 00:28:32,875
Engage hostile targets
as they appear.

247
00:28:32,943 --> 00:28:36,435
Deadly force is authorized.
How copy? Over.

248
00:28:36,513 --> 00:28:39,073
Red Man, Trans Six Actual.
Negative, negative!

249
00:28:39,149 --> 00:28:41,845
Be advised, I have women
and children in my line of fire.

250
00:28:41,918 --> 00:28:44,751
I got snipers in the buildings
at 400 meters. How copy? Over.

251
00:28:44,821 --> 00:28:48,882
What is it about this order
you don't understand, Captain Lee?

252
00:28:48,959 --> 00:28:51,894
Sir, are you ordering me
to fire into the crowd? Over.

253
00:28:51,962 --> 00:28:54,624
Yes, goddamn it!
Waste the motherfuckers!

254
00:28:54,698 --> 00:28:57,633
Six out.
Engage! Engage!

255
00:28:57,701 --> 00:29:01,137
Open fire!

256
00:29:07,144 --> 00:29:10,079
[Screaming]

257
00:29:20,857 --> 00:29:24,486
Cease fire!

258
00:29:24,561 --> 00:29:26,654
Cease fire!

259
00:29:26,730 --> 00:29:28,823
Cease fire!

260
00:29:28,899 --> 00:29:31,663
Stay down! There may still be
snipers out there.

261
00:29:31,735 --> 00:29:33,828
Cease fire!

262
00:29:33,904 --> 00:29:37,670
- Cease fire, goddamn it!
- <i>Everybody stay down!</i>

263
00:29:37,741 --> 00:29:42,371
There may still be snipers
out there. Stay down!

264
00:29:42,445 --> 00:29:44,379
<i>Get down!</i>

265
00:30:26,590 --> 00:30:29,024
[Wailing]

266
00:30:32,963 --> 00:30:34,897
<i>[Woman Screaming]</i>

267
00:30:41,004 --> 00:30:42,938
- Sergeant Mac.
- <i>[Mac] Sir?</i>

268
00:30:43,006 --> 00:30:46,339
Contact all stations.
Mission complete.

269
00:30:46,409 --> 00:30:50,675
Launch medevacs.
Dead and wounded out first.

270
00:30:50,747 --> 00:30:52,681
<i>Aye, Colonel.</i>

271
00:30:52,749 --> 00:30:57,379
<i>All stations, this is Red Man.</i>
<i>Mission complete.</i>

272
00:30:57,454 --> 00:31:01,185
<i>Move all medevacs to L.Z.</i>
<i>How copy? Over.</i>

273
00:31:01,524 --> 00:31:03,389
<i>[Car Horn Honks]</i>

274
00:31:07,030 --> 00:31:08,964
<i>[Siren Blaring]</i>

275
00:31:17,874 --> 00:31:19,307
<i>[Man]</i>
<i>The F.B.I. Investigation shows...</i>

276
00:31:19,376 --> 00:31:21,776
<i>that all the bullet holes</i>
<i>in the embassy wall...</i>

277
00:31:21,845 --> 00:31:24,871
<i>came from directly across</i>
<i>the way, from the snipers.</i>

278
00:31:24,948 --> 00:31:28,076
Any weapons or ammo found
among the dead or wounded?

279
00:31:28,151 --> 00:31:31,780
<i>No, sir. Nothing.</i>
<i>However, intelligence suggests...</i>

280
00:31:31,855 --> 00:31:34,289
this could have been
a terrorist operation.

281
00:31:34,357 --> 00:31:36,291
Any proof?

282
