490
00:44:30,084 --> 00:44:32,177
The guy's
a real marine, Dad.

491
00:44:32,253 --> 00:44:34,949
I mean, if they
can do this to him...

492
00:44:35,023 --> 00:44:38,390
just hang him out to dry...
they can do it to anybody.

493
00:44:38,459 --> 00:44:42,452
Forget that he's my friend.
They can do it to anybody.

494
00:44:42,530 --> 00:44:45,021
That means your medals
and your citations...

495
00:44:45,099 --> 00:44:48,068
won't mean jack shit
when they come after you.

496
00:44:51,806 --> 00:44:54,274
<i>[Metal Clinking]</i>

497
00:44:54,609 --> 00:44:56,873
At least two of his own guys
are gonna testify...

498
00:44:56,945 --> 00:44:59,743
that he didn't have
to open fire, sir.

499
00:44:59,814 --> 00:45:03,750
Nobody reports seeing any
weapons among the demonstrators.

500
00:45:03,818 --> 00:45:06,981
- His psych eval was a disaster.
- What about embassy footage?

501
00:45:07,055 --> 00:45:09,489
Cameras, film, videotape,
home movies, shit like that?

502
00:45:09,557 --> 00:45:14,654
No, I've subpoenaed everything.
The embassy got hit pretty good.

503
00:45:14,729 --> 00:45:18,096
- Most of it was destroyed.
- <i>[Door Opens]</i>

504
00:45:18,166 --> 00:45:20,100
<i>[Man Grunting]</i>

505
00:45:22,470 --> 00:45:24,870
Terry, you know Tom Chandler. He's
