506
00:45:24,939 --> 00:45:28,602
Colonel Childers, good to see
you again, sir. Um, all right.

507
00:45:28,676 --> 00:45:32,578
First, we've subpoenaed all
the Article 32 investigator's notes,

508
00:45:32,647 --> 00:45:34,581
