655
00:53:40,501 --> 00:53:42,594
Got your word on that?

656
00:53:43,704 --> 00:53:45,638
[Sighs]
Oh, shit.

657
00:53:45,706 --> 00:53:48,368
They take my uniform away,
they may as well shoot me.

658
00:53:48,442 --> 00:53:52,606
You can live with it, bud.
Believe me.

659
00:53:53,848 --> 00:53:57,079
I'm not gonna shit you.
